title: Costume party! 2016 candidates ready for Halloween
text:
Costume party! 2016 candidates ready for Halloween The Des Moines Register 10:16 a.m. CDT October 19, 2015 Buy Photo Which candidate costume do you like best? (Photo: Mark Marturello/Register illustration) Buy Photo 
Iowans are used to seeing presidential candidates in their finest business attire. 
Mark Marturello, the Register’s award-winning illustrator, thought it would be fun to see them wearing something a little more casual —OK, a LOT more casual. 
Enjoy the candidates’ costumes in this Halloween-themed illustration. 
BONUS: For more Halloween fun, use our jack-o-lantern stencils to carve a few presidential-inspired pumpkins! We have patterns for every major Democrat and Republican candidate. Read or Share this story: http://dmreg.co/1LGihLz TOP VIDEOS
